description: Hank, writer, impresario, photographer, record producer, knew Bob Wilber well, and celebrates his versatility in the second half of this interview.  Recorded by Michael Steinman for JAZZ LIVES (http://www.jazzlives.wordpress.com) at Hank's office in downtown Manhattan, August 27, 2019.
